name: There is something in my chest
description:
Piece #7 of the collection:
I'm not your therapist but I'd like to cheer you up with my dorky art

The series focuses on the fragility of the inner world and brings up topics that we often find in our long journey on earth. 

#7
There is something in my chest. It is some sort of pain, but not physical pain. It's the weight of some emotions that I can't understand.
